cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper deals with automatic retouching of photos using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of reinforcement learning also suggests the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also involves image processing and graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
